
            Video
            Frances Bishop: ‘I learnt more as a barmaid than at university’
            Frances Bishop doesn’t think higher education is for everyone. In fact, she says dropping out of uni and working behind a bar helped her build the Pud Store, a successful designer childrenswear boutique. This video has been optimised for mobile viewing on the BBC News app. The BBC News app is available from the Apple App Store for iPhone and Google Play Store for Android.
                
                        06 Nov 2018
                    
                
        
